information: José María Lázaro S.A., better known for its brand names, TAISI and FALAGUERA, is dedicated to producing tinned fruit. We are located in the municipality of Calatayud (province of Zaragoza). We have a great deal of experience in this sector with three generations in the business. TAISI provides a wide range of products for the food industry, such as crystallised fruit, fruit in syrup, jams and disguised and treated with sulphite.
